es":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9Jv","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":25415,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/11\/13\/salat-shortened-two-rakaat-travel\/","url_meta":{"origin":37417,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Travel: Prayer shortened to two cycles during travel","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 13, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: I accompanied the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and during travel he would not add more to his prayer than two cycles. Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman did likewise, may Allah be pleased with them. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1051, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 689 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33739,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/20\/sahaba-criticized-united\/","url_meta":{"origin":37417,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Ikhtilaf: Companions criticized leadership but remained united","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 20, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdur Rahman ibn Yazid reported: Uthman, may Allah be pleased with him, prayed four cycles at Mina. Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud said, \u201cI prayed it as two cycles with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, as well as Abu Bakr and Umar.\u201d Mu\u2019awiyah ibn Qurrah added: Abdullah then prayed\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18569,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/18\/saeed-prayer-different-sunnah\/","url_meta":{"origin":37417,"position":2},"title":"Sa\u2019id on Sunnah: Punished for praying differently from Sunnah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 18, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019id ibn al-Musayyib reported: He saw a man praying after sunrise at dawn with more than two cycles, and he was excessive in his bowing and prostration, so Sa'id prohibited him. The man said, \u201cO Abu Muhammad, will Allah punish us for praying?\u201d Sa\u2019id said, \u201cNo, but he will punish\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27620,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/16\/break-fast-intending-travel\/","url_meta":{"origin":37417,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Travel: Permission to break fast before intending to travel","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 16, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Muhammad ibn Ka\u2019b reported: I came to Anas ibn Malik, may Allah be pleased with him, during Ramadan and he intended to travel. His mount was prepared for him and he put on his traveling clothes. He called for some food and he ate it. I said to him, \u201cIs\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25413,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/11\/13\/shorten-prayers-travel\/","url_meta":{"origin":37417,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Travel: Permission to shorten prayers during travel","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 13, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: We went out with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, from Medina to Mecca and he would pray two cycles\u00a0at a time until he returned. Yahya ibn Abi Ishaq said, \u201cHow long did he remain in Mecca?\u201d Anas said, \u201cTen days.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33674,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/02\/12-rakaat-al-sunan-al-rawatib\/","url_meta":{"origin":37417,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sunnah: Twelve raka\u2019at of al-Sunan al-Rawatib prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever perseveres in performing twelve cycles of prayer from the Sunnah, Allah will build a house for him in Paradise. They are four cycles before noon prayer and two after it, two cycles after sunset prayer, two\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/37417","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"htt